%% Purchase Requisition → Purchase Order → GRN → Invoice Workflow
%% Rahah24 ERP - Inventory Management System
%% Last Updated: October 25, 2025

flowchart TD
    START[Purchase Need Identified]

    START --> CREATE_PR[Department Head<br/>Creates Purchase Requisition]
    CREATE_PR --> PR_DETAILS[Enter PR Details:<br/>- Items & quantities<br/>- Justification<br/>- Required date<br/>- Priority]

    PR_DETAILS --> CALC_AMOUNT[Calculate Total Amount]
    CALC_AMOUNT --> ROUTE_APPROVAL{Determine<br/>Approval Level}

    ROUTE_APPROVAL -->|Amount < PKR 50,000| L1_APPROVE[Level 1 Approver<br/>Review & Approve]
    ROUTE_APPROVAL -->|PKR 50,001 - 200,000| L2_APPROVE[Level 2 Approver<br/>Review & Approve]
    ROUTE_APPROVAL -->|Amount > PKR 200,000| L3_APPROVE[Level 3 Approver<br/>Review & Approve]

    L1_APPROVE --> L1_DECISION{L1 Decision}
    L2_APPROVE --> L2_DECISION{L2 Decision}
    L3_APPROVE --> L3_DECISION{L3 Decision}

    L1_DECISION -->|Approved| PR_APPROVED[PR Approved]
    L1_DECISION -->|Rejected| PR_REJECTED[PR Rejected<br/>Reason documented]
    L2_DECISION -->|Approved| PR_APPROVED
    L2_DECISION -->|Rejected| PR_REJECTED
    L3_DECISION -->|Approved| PR_APPROVED
    L3_DECISION -->|Rejected| PR_REJECTED

    PR_REJECTED --> NOTIFY_REQUESTER[Notify Department Head<br/>Email + In-App Alert]
    NOTIFY_REQUESTER --> END_REJECTED[End: PR Rejected]

    PR_APPROVED --> CREATE_PO[Purchasing Officer<br/>Creates Purchase Order]
    CREATE_PO --> SELECT_VENDOR[Select Vendor:<br/>- Price comparison<br/>- Performance rating<br/>- Payment terms]

    SELECT_VENDOR --> ENTER_PO[Enter PO Details:<br/>- Vendor details<br/>- Delivery date<br/>- Payment terms<br/>- Line items with prices]

    ENTER_PO --> PRICE_CHECK{Check Price<br/>Variance}
    PRICE_CHECK -->|Variance ≤ 5%| PO_ROUTE_NORMAL[Route to Normal Approval]
    PRICE_CHECK -->|Variance 5-10%| PO_ROUTE_L2[Route to L2<br/>for Variance Approval]
    PRICE_CHECK -->|Variance > 10%| PO_ROUTE_L3[Route to L3<br/>for Variance Approval]

    PO_ROUTE_NORMAL --> PO_AMOUNT_CHECK{PO Amount<br/>Check}
    PO_AMOUNT_CHECK -->|< PKR 50,000| PO_L1[L1 Approver]
    PO_AMOUNT_CHECK -->|< PKR 200,000| PO_L2[L2 Approver]
    PO_AMOUNT_CHECK -->|≥ PKR 200,000| PO_L3[L3 Approver]

    PO_L1 --> PO_DECISION{PO Decision}
    PO_L2 --> PO_DECISION
    PO_L3 --> PO_DECISION
    PO_ROUTE_L2 --> PO_L2
    PO_ROUTE_L3 --> PO_L3

    PO_DECISION -->|Approved| PO_APPROVED[PO Approved]
    PO_DECISION -->|Rejected| PO_REJECTED[PO Rejected<br/>Return to Purchasing]
    PO_REJECTED --> SELECT_VENDOR

    PO_APPROVED --> SEND_PO[Send PO to Vendor<br/>Email + PDF]
    SEND_PO --> VENDOR_PROCESS[Vendor Processes Order]

    VENDOR_PROCESS --> VENDOR_DELIVERY[Vendor Delivers Goods<br/>with Invoice]
    VENDOR_DELIVERY --> RECEIVE_GOODS[Store Keeper<br/>Receives Goods]

    RECEIVE_GOODS --> CREATE_GRN[Create Goods Receipt Note<br/>- GRN number generated<br/>- Link to PO<br/>- Vendor invoice details]

    CREATE_GRN --> INSPECT_GOODS{Inspect Goods<br/>Quality Check}
    INSPECT_GOODS -->|Quality Pass| ACCEPT_ALL[Accept All Items]
    INSPECT_GOODS -->|Quality Fail| PARTIAL_REJECT{Partial or<br/>Full Reject?}
    PARTIAL_REJECT -->|Partial| ACCEPT_PARTIAL[Accept Good Items<br/>Reject Defective]
    PARTIAL_REJECT -->|Full| REJECT_ALL[Reject All Items<br/>Return to Vendor]

    REJECT_ALL --> NOTIFY_VENDOR_REJECT[Notify Vendor<br/>Debit Note]
    NOTIFY_VENDOR_REJECT --> END_REJECTED_GRN[End: GRN Rejected]

    ACCEPT_ALL --> CREATE_BATCHES[Create Item Batches<br/>- Batch numbers<br/>- Expiry dates<br/>- Mfg dates]
    ACCEPT_PARTIAL --> CREATE_BATCHES

    CREATE_BATCHES --> UPDATE_LOCATION[Assign Storage Location<br/>Zone-Aisle-Rack-Bin]
    UPDATE_LOCATION --> POST_GRN[Post GRN]

    POST_GRN --> UPDATE_STOCK[Update Stock Levels:<br/>- Current stock +<br/>- Available stock +<br/>- Weighted average cost]

    UPDATE_STOCK --> CREATE_STOCK_MOVEMENT[Create Stock Movement<br/>Type: PURCHASE<br/>Reference: GRN]

    CREATE_STOCK_MOVEMENT --> INVOICE_MATCH[Finance: 3-Way Match<br/>PO ↔ GRN ↔ Invoice]
    INVOICE_MATCH --> MATCH_CHECK{Match<br/>Successful?}

    MATCH_CHECK -->|Yes - Perfect Match| CREATE_GL[Create Journal Entry<br/>Dr: Inventory Asset<br/>Cr: Accounts Payable]
    MATCH_CHECK -->|Discrepancy| FLAG_REVIEW[Flag for Finance Review<br/>Price/Quantity mismatch]

    FLAG_REVIEW --> RESOLVE_DISC[Finance Resolves<br/>Discrepancy]
    RESOLVE_DISC --> CREATE_GL

    CREATE_GL --> SCHEDULE_PAYMENT[Schedule Payment:<br/>- Cash immediate<br/>- Credit based on terms<br/>- Bank transfer]

    SCHEDULE_PAYMENT --> PROCESS_PAYMENT[Process Payment<br/>to Vendor]
    PROCESS_PAYMENT --> UPDATE_VENDOR_PERF[Update Vendor Performance:<br/>- On-time delivery<br/>- Quality rating<br/>- Price compliance]

    UPDATE_VENDOR_PERF --> TRIGGER_ALERTS{Trigger<br/>Alerts?}
    TRIGGER_ALERTS -->|Stock at Reorder Level| ALERT_REORDER[Alert: Reorder Suggested]
    TRIGGER_ALERTS -->|Stock Over Maximum| ALERT_OVER[Alert: Over Stock]
    TRIGGER_ALERTS -->|Expiry < 30 Days| ALERT_EXPIRY[Alert: Expiry Warning]
    TRIGGER_ALERTS -->|None| END_SUCCESS[End: Purchase Complete ✓]

    ALERT_REORDER --> END_SUCCESS
    ALERT_OVER --> END_SUCCESS
    ALERT_EXPIRY --> END_SUCCESS

    style START fill:#e1f5e1
    style PR_APPROVED fill:#c8e6c9
    style PO_APPROVED fill:#c8e6c9
